data.description: Come enjoy the peace and quiet of this Pinecrest Estates. This 2 bedroom 2 bath home sits on lots and has a large back deck to enjoy those peacefully evenings. There is detached shop large enough to park a car or other motorized  vehicle in. The covered parking is perfect to keep your cars out of the heat. The home is in move in condition and waiting on its new owners. This neighborhood also includes boat ramp, pier, and swimming pool for your enjoyment.
